---
// Final CTA / contact
---

<section id="contact" class="section cta-section">
  <div class="container cta-inner">
    <h2>Ready to ride the first usable jet?</h2>
    <p>Request a demo, configure your drive, or talk to us about integration. We ship inboard, outboard, and pod systems across Europe.</p>
    <div class="cta-actions">
      <a href="mailto:hi@sylents.de" class="btn">hi@sylents.de</a>
      <a href="tel:+4976639317996" class="btn btn-ghost">+49 7663 9317-996</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
.cta-section {
  text-align: center;
  background: var(--color-bg-section);
  border-top: 1px solid var(--color-border);
}
.cta-inner { max-width: 640px; }
.cta-inner h2 { margin-bottom: 1rem; }
.cta-inner p {
  font-size: 1.1rem;
  margin-bottom: 2rem;
}
.cta-actions {
  display: flex;
  gap: 1rem;
  justify-content: center;
  flex-wrap: wrap;
}
</style>
